OL,6,FA decision has been made not to
OL,7,Fintroduce birthing facilities the
OL,8,FGalloway Community Hospital, leaving
OL,9,Fpregnant women with a long diversion
OL,10,Fto get to the nearest facility.
OL,12,FThe Dumfries and Galloway Integration
OL,13,FJoint Board made the decision
OL,14,Ffollowing an independently-led review
OL,15,Fand public consultation.
OL,17,FThe home birthing model will be
OL,18,Fretained "for the foreseeable future."
