OL,6,FChairman of the IJB (Integration Joint
OL,7,FBoard) Andy McFarlane said: "One thing
OL,8,FI would want to stress from the start
OL,9,Fis our confidence as a Board in the
OL,10,Fmaternity services as they stand
OL,11,Fcurrently across the region, including
OL,12,FWigtownshire.
OL,14,F"It was acknowledged that care is of a
OL,15,Fvery high standard, and it was noted
OL,16,Fthat there is an enhanced offer
OL,17,Fdelivered through the Oak Tree Family
OL,18,FCentre."
