OL,6,FThe decision to retain the current
OL,7,Fmodel he says was "not an easy one"
OL,8,Fand that it is due to "staff
OL,9,Fshortages."
OL,11,FHe said: "The decision about provision
OL,12,Fof birthing services in Wigtownshire
OL,13,Fwas not an easy one to arrive at, as
OL,14,Fevery member of the board is acutely
OL,15,Faware of calls from communities to
OL,16,Fhave the fullest range of services
OL,17,Fmade available locally.
