OL,3,CDecision made to keep no maternity
OL,4,Cfacilities in Wigtownshire
OL,6,F"We were fully informed, thanks to the
OL,7,Freview and the consultation, of the
OL,8,Fissues faced by expectant mothers in
OL,9,Fterms of travelling to give birth in
OL,10,FDumfries.
OL,12,F"This is a situation which dates from
OL,13,F2018, when birthing services within
OL,14,FGalloway Community Hospital were
OL,15,Fsuspended on a temporary basis due to
OL,16,Funexpected staff shortages."
OL,18,FAndy explained how the current model
OL,19,Fis the best one they could have in
OL,20,Fplace.
