OL,4,Cfacilities in Wigtownshire
OL,6,FHe said: "Taking on board the original
OL,7,Freport, all of the facts, and all of
OL,8,Fthe thoughts and perspectives, the IJB
OL,9,Fconcluded that the status quo
OL,10,Frepresents the best and most
OL,11,Fdeliverable and sustainable model now
OL,12,Fand for the foreseeable future.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
