OL,3,CDecision made to keep no maternity
OL,4,Cfacilities in Wigtownshire
OL,6,F"Introducing this service at Galloway
OL,7,FCommunity Hospital for what would be a
OL,8,Fsmall number of eligible expectant
OL,9,Fmothers would not represent a
OL,10,Fsignificant difference from a home
OL,11,Fbirth, as the resources in terms of
OL,12,Fmidwifery staff who would be on hand
OL,13,Fto provide support would be exactly
OL,14,Fthe same. Only the setting would
OL,15,Fchange.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
