OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F351A1727269247
OL,3,CDecision made to keep no maternity
OL,4,Cfacilities in Wigtownshire
OL,6,F"And while we would ideally want to
OL,7,Foffer an option of a hospital birth
OL,8,Fwhich does not require travelling to
OL,9,FDumfries, we recognised that neither
OL,10,Fapproach would actually end this
OL,11,Frequirement for the majority of
OL,12,Fexpectant mothers.
OL,14,F"We also considered what was
OL,15,Fdeliverable safely at present, and the
OL,16,Ffact that both across the region and
OL,17,Fnationally there is a routine
OL,18,Frequirement on mothers to make
OL,19,Fsometimes quite lengthy journeys to
OL,20,Flocations where birthing services can
OL,21,Fbe provided.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
