PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F351A1727269247
OL,3,CDecision made to keep no maternity
OL,4,Cfacilities in Wigtownshire
OL,6,F"This has been a challenging decision
OL,7,Fon what is a very personal and
OL,8,Femotional subject, where there is
OL,9,Fgreat strength of feeling, and where
OL,10,Fwe as a Board recognise a commitment
OL,11,Fto patient-centred care.
OL,13,F"In conclusion, the Board agreed that
OL,14,Fthe approach which serves the majority
OL,15,Fof expectant mothers in Wigtownshire
OL,16,Fis the one which is reasonable and
OL,17,Fappropriate for all, but with that
OL,18,Fcontinuing option of home birth."
